============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

DIGITAL_TWIN_ENABLED=true
DIGITAL_TWIN_MODE=advisory
DIGITAL_TWIN_DRY_RUN=true
DIGITAL_TWIN_REQUIRE_EVIDENCE=true
DIGITAL_TWIN_MAX_GRAPH_NODES=5000
DIGITAL_TWIN_MAX_GRAPH_EDGES=20000

IMPACT_PROPAGATION_ENABLED=true
BLAST_RADIUS_ANALYSIS_ENABLED=true
TWIN_SNAPSHOT_ENABLED=true
TWIN_REPORTS_ENABLED=true

MACRO_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
MACRO_SIMULATION_DRY_RUN=true
MACRO_SIMULATION_MAX_RUNS_PER_REQUEST=10
MARKET_SHOCK_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
POLICY_SCENARIO_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
SUPPLY_DEMAND_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
REGIONAL_SCENARIO_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true

CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_ENABLED=true
CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_MODE=advisory
CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_DRY_RUN=true
CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true
CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_CYCLE_INTERVAL_DAYS=7

STRATEGY_MEMORY_ENABLED=true
DECISION_LINEAGE_ENABLED=true
STRATEGIC_TRADEOFF_ENABLED=true
ROADMAP_SIMULATION_ENABLED=true
STRATEGY_WAR_ROOM_ENABLED=true
WAR_ROOM_MAX_ACTIVE_SESSIONS=10

Rules:
- Digital twin must be advisory and dry-run by default.
- Macro simulation must be dry-run by default.
- Continuous planning recommendations must require human approval.
- Strategy War Room must never execute operational changes directly.
- All scenario outputs must include confidence, assumptions, evidence, limitations, and risk notes.
- Raw confidential data must not be stored in graph nodes, reports, scenario packs, or war room transcripts.
- Graph size limits must prevent runaway memory usage.

