============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- DIGITAL_TWIN_DISABLED
- TWIN_ENTITY_NOT_FOUND
- TWIN_RELATIONSHIP_NOT_FOUND
- TWIN_GRAPH_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
- IMPACT_SIMULATION_FAILED
- BLAST_RADIUS_FAILED
- MACRO_SIMULATION_DISABLED
- MACRO_SCENARIO_NOT_FOUND
- MACRO_SCENARIO_FAILED
- POLICY_SCENARIO_TEMPLATE_ONLY
- SCENARIO_PACK_NOT_FOUND
- CONTINUOUS_PLANNING_DISABLED
- PLANNING_CYCLE_NOT_FOUND
- STRATEGY_MEMORY_NOT_FOUND
- DECISION_LINEAGE_NOT_FOUND
- TRADEOFF_NOT_FOUND
- PLANNING_RECOMMENDATION_NOT_FOUND
- WAR_ROOM_SESSION_NOT_FOUND
- ADVISORY_ONLY_ACTION
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

